{"tid":2200421,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"[特發]Mox 金屬卡名額加到20,000張","createTime":"2020-09-13T03:25:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-13T05:39:53.000Z","uid":364562,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"221c20a12276dfc295228ed3fe2a85f60c403a0f","tid":2200421,"uid":364562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T03:25:18.000Z","msg":"感謝你參與Mox的創始成員登記推廣活動。由於活動反應十分熱烈，遠超過首3,000個限量版金屬Mox Card名額，我們於較早前已確認首3,000名成功登記人士的金屬Mox Card資格。<br />\n<br />\n同時，Mox十分感激20,000多位朋友的登記。為答謝大家的支持，我們很高興地宣布，在2020年5月4日至6月30日*期間於我們網站登記，並於稍後成功開立Mox戶口的朋友，都會獲得金屬Mox Card。"},{"pid":"47b21d36b17c7d49b1d3978a3a4958bd319970f5","tid":2200421,"uid":100151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T03:34:00.000Z","msg":"Old news is so funny"},{"pid":"a346a45dd01e0ea52f390484ff7994395cd34b00","tid":2200421,"uid":14716,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T05:17:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />笑死 金屬卡打飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbf453e0d19c7ac2cb2b08a29a22d03512b2f8d6","tid":2200421,"uid":35408,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T05:22:08.000Z","msg":"拎嚟做咩<br />\n拎住會高尚啲咩"},{"pid":"8ba373951a7cc868f6cc5818c05a2ec9a2e7c702","tid":2200421,"uid":367327,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T05:39:53.000Z","msg":"有錢人先唔會稀罕張黑卡特登走去撲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}